      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Caméras HomeKit (alpha)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Native Swift HAP server. Each Frigate camera shows up as a motion sensor in Apple Home.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Serveur HAP natif Swift. Chaque caméra Frigate apparaît comme un capteur de mouvement dans Apple Home."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "HomeKit bridge is off. Toggle on to start pairing.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le bridge HomeKit est désactivé. Activez-le pour démarrer l’appairage."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Off. Toggle on to start the HAP server and pair from Apple Home.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Désactivé. Activez pour démarrer le serveur HAP et appairer depuis Apple Home."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Off. First-run install bootstraps homebridge + homebridge-camera-ffmpeg via npm (~30-90s).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Désactivé. La première activation installe homebridge + homebridge-camera-ffmpeg via npm (~30-90 s)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cameras off. Toggle on to install Homebridge and start streaming.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Caméras désactivées. Activez pour installer Homebridge et démarrer la diffusion."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Find this under Frigate → Settings → MQTT. Defaults to port 1883 (no TLS).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Disponible dans Frigate → Settings → MQTT. Port 1883 par défaut (sans TLS)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Leave blank if your Mosquitto / EMQX broker allows anonymous connections (Frigate's default).": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Laissez vide si votre broker Mosquitto / EMQX accepte les connexions anonymes (par défaut chez Frigate)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Frigate publishes detection events to an MQTT broker (usually Mosquitto). The Bridge subscribes to those events and forwards them to your iCloud account.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Frigate publie les événements de détection vers un broker MQTT (en général Mosquitto). Le Bridge s’y abonne et les transfère vers votre compte iCloud."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Lumen Bridge connects your Frigate NVR directly to Apple's ecosystem — push notifications, HomeKit cameras, iCloud clip storage — without any third-party server in between.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lumen Bridge connecte votre NVR Frigate directement à l’écosystème Apple — notifications push, caméras HomeKit, stockage des clips dans iCloud — sans serveur tiers intermédiaire."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "When enabled, the Bridge fetches the finalised clip from Frigate and attaches it to the FrigateEvent record. Clips are 1-10 MB each — leaving this off saves iCloud storage.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Lorsque activé, le Bridge récupère le clip finalisé depuis Frigate et l’attache à l’enregistrement FrigateEvent. Chaque clip pèse 1 à 10 Mo — désactivez pour économiser l’espace iCloud."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Distribution note: this feature requires a non-sandboxed direct-download build. The TestFlight build doesn't have permission to spawn the Homebridge subprocess.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Note de distribution : cette fonctionnalité requiert une version directe sans sandbox. La version TestFlight n’a pas l’autorisation de lancer le sous-processus Homebridge."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "HomeKit cameras run on the macOS Bridge. Your Apple TV inherits the Frigate connection automatically — pair the cameras from any iOS device under the same Apple ID.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les caméras HomeKit s’exécutent sur le Bridge macOS. Votre Apple TV hérite automatiquement de la connexion Frigate — appairez les caméras depuis n’importe quel appareil iOS sous le même identifiant Apple."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No instances discovered via Bonjour yet. If your Frigate is on a different VLAN or doesn't advertise `_frigate._tcp`, just enter the host above manually.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Aucune instance détectée via Bonjour pour l’instant. Si votre Frigate est sur un autre VLAN ou n’annonce pas `_frigate._tcp`, saisissez l’hôte manuellement ci-dessus."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Detection events are stored in your private iCloud database, scoped to the `iCloud.com.lorislabapp.lumenbridge` container. Only your Apple ID can read them.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Les événements de détection sont stockés dans votre base iCloud privée, dans le conteneur `iCloud.com.lorislabapp.lumenbridge`. Seul votre identifiant Apple peut les lire."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Bridge is designed to grow into your home's full Frigate ↔ Apple control panel. Here's what's already live and what's next.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le Bridge est conçu pour devenir le panneau de contrôle complet entre Frigate et Apple chez vous. Voici ce qui est déjà disponible et ce qui arrive."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The Bridge is running in your menu bar. As Frigate detects events, you'll get notifications on your iPhone, iPad, Mac, and Watch — no server in between.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le Bridge tourne dans votre barre de menus. À mesure que Frigate détecte des événements, vous recevrez des notifications sur votre iPhone, iPad, Mac et Watch — sans serveur intermédiaire."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Phase 5 v0.2 — uses a bundled Homebridge sidecar with homebridge-camera-ffmpeg. RTSP streams come from Frigate's go2rtc on port 8554. First-run install ~30-90s.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Phase 5 v0.2 — utilise un sidecar Homebridge intégré avec homebridge-camera-ffmpeg. Les flux RTSP proviennent du go2rtc de Frigate sur le port 8554. Installation initiale ~30-90 s."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open Apple Home → Add Accessory → enter this code. The cameras bridge appears as ‘Lumen Bridge Cameras’ — separate from the motion-sensor bridge above.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Ouvrez Apple Home → Ajouter un accessoire → saisissez ce code. Le bridge des caméras apparaît sous le nom « Lumen Bridge Cameras » — distinct du bridge de capteurs de mouvement ci-dessus."
          }
        }
      }
    },
